# Order Fulfillment

This domain is in charge of the catalog, inventory, customers orering, shipping and receiving.

Concepts in this domain include:

- Customer
- Add to cart
- Procede to checkout
- Order
- Packability
- Packing
- Shipping
- Stock on hand
- Replenish

